#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/dynamic_chunk_pipeline_parallel.md:1
msgid "Dynamic Chunked Pipeline Parallel"
msgstr "动态分块流水线并行"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/dynamic_chunk_pipeline_parallel.md:4
msgid ""
"For design details and mathematical models, see [Design "
"Document](../../developer_guide/Design_Documents/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md)."
" For deployment tutorial, see [Dynamic Chunked Pipeline Parallel "
"Tutorial](../../tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md)."
msgstr "设计细节和数学模型请参见[设计文档](../../developer_guide/Design_Documents/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md)。部署教程请参见[动态分块流水线并行教程](../../tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md)。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/dynamic_chunk_pipeline_parallel.md:7
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/dynamic_chunk_pipeline_parallel.md:9
msgid ""
"Dynamic Chunked Pipeline Parallel (CPP) is a profiling-based dynamic "
"chunking strategy that optimizes prefill performance for long sequences "
"in Pipeline Parallelism (PP) scenarios."
msgstr "动态分块流水线并行（CPP）是一种基于性能分析的动态分块策略，用于优化流水线并行（PP）场景中长序列的预填充性能。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/dynamic_chunk_pipeline_parallel.md:11
msgid "When to Use"
msgstr "使用场景"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/dynamic_chunk_pipeline_parallel.md:13
msgid ""
"**Variable-length sequence serving**: PP does not introduce degradation "
"on short sequences, and gains benefits through dynamic chunks on long "
"sequences."
msgstr "**变长序列服务**：PP对短序列不会引入性能退化，并通过长序列的动态分块获得收益。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/dynamic_chunk_pipeline_parallel.md:14
msgid ""
"**Ultra-long sequence inference**: For sequences exceeding single-machine"
" memory capacity (e.g., 1M tokens), dynamic chunking significantly "
"reduces pipeline idle time."
msgstr "**超长序列推理**：对于超出单机内存容量的序列（如1M tokens），动态分块可显著减少流水线空闲时间。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/dynamic_chunk_pipeline_parallel.md:16
msgid "Supported Scenarios"
msgstr "支持场景"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/dynamic_chunk_pipeline_parallel.md:18
msgid ""
